sentences: David Gogokhia (Georgian: დავით გოგოხია, born 16 July 1987 in Jvari, Georgia) is a Georgian experimental visual artist, director of photography, and video editor, specialize in music videos, commercials etc
After graduating from Georgian Technical University in 2008, he began working as a web designer for a while.
